milestones.description: Allan Donald and Fanie de Villiers's 10-run partnership is SA's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 9 between Allan Donald and McMillan
Peter Kirsten has broken the record for most sixes (6) in ODIs for SA, going past Hansie Cronje's 5
This is the highest match aggregate (418) involving teams South Africa & Pakistan in ODIs
